.TH "xcsi2rxss_soft_reset" 9 "xcsi2rxss_soft_reset" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
xcsi2rxss_soft_reset \- Does a soft reset of the MIPI CSI-2 Rx Subsystem
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" xcsi2rxss_soft_reset
.BI "(struct xcsi2rxss_state *state "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "state" 12
Xilinx CSI-2 Rx Subsystem structure pointer
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Core takes less than 100 video clock cycles to reset.
So a larger timeout value is chosen for margin.
.SH "RETURN"
0 - on success OR -ETIME if reset times out
